Actually, in the previous three,

00:14.560 --> 00:18.000
even when, as they say,
the shit hit the fan,

00:18.280 --> 00:20.559
you managed to hold it together.

00:20.679 --> 00:23.879
-I didn't have to talk about my own shit.
