with an identical look to Fede's.

19:11.920 --> 19:15.440
Leo is afraid it's a doctor
taking his temperature.

19:15.519 --> 19:17.559
They'll be sweet, with matching clothes.

19:17.799 --> 19:21.319
When we meet next time,
with Donatella, you'll try them all.

19:21.400 --> 19:25.440
On the back of Fede's shirt,
there are four initials,

19:25.519 --> 19:30.000
F for "Federico," C for "Chiara,"
L for "Leone," and V for "Vittoria."

19:30.319 --> 19:31.799
-Hello, baby.
-Hi.

19:31.920 --> 19:33.039
What's wrong?

19:33.079 --> 19:36.079
It'll be the baby's name.
You guys already know it,

19:36.200 --> 19:38.079
by the time you watch this.

19:38.160 --> 19:39.240
I'll have a look.

19:39.759 --> 19:42.440
-So beautiful!
-Beautiful!

19:43.400 --> 19:45.079
Really beautiful.

19:46.240 --> 19:47.880
I like the detail on the back.

19:47.960 --> 19:51.720
Leo was convinced
that the tailor was a doctor,

19:51.799 --> 19:54.519
so he just would not allow himself
to be measured.

19:54.559 --> 19:55.640
No, Mommy!

19:55.720 --> 19:58.039
It was super stressful.

19:58.079 --> 19:59.720
She's taking your...

20:02.319 --> 20:04.240
-Leo.
-Give me your hand, look.

20:04.559 --> 20:08.000
Come on,
I'll leave you under the table, look.

20:08.799 --> 20:12.559
-It's over, baby, it's over.
-It's over.

20:12.640 --> 20:14.640
Why don't you like it?

20:14.720 --> 20:17.440
I don't like it
when they take the measurements!

20:17.519 --> 20:20.279
But we're done!
You don't have to do it anymore!

20:20.880 --> 20:23.720
-Daddy is doing it.
-It hurts!

20:23.799 --> 20:27.319
-How can it hurt, love?
-They send people to jail for that, honey.

20:32.440 --> 20:35.400
Today we're going
to record the theme song.

20:37.720 --> 20:40.319
-How spontaneous.
-Do you wanna add anything?

20:40.440 --> 20:43.799
You were so spontaneous
that I don't want to add anything else.

20:43.920 --> 20:44.920
Exactly.

20:45.759 --> 20:48.519
I'm super anxious today because

20:48.559 --> 20:52.960
