means leaving my comfort zone.

20:53.160 --> 20:54.279
We're ready.

20:54.319 --> 20:56.519
I only did it once with Baby K.

20:57.079 --> 20:59.759
I was less nervous, and it came out well.

21:00.319 --> 21:01.960
I don't know how it'll go,

21:02.039 --> 21:04.240
