didn't make much sense.

21:18.640 --> 21:23.319
-Baby, I have some variants on the hook.
-I lost the thing.

21:23.440 --> 21:28.200
The original lyrics read,
"Chiara thought I was a gigolo."

21:29.319 --> 21:32.559
-Can you explain?
-So, wait, I have the two lyrics.

21:32.680 --> 21:35.799
"I texted Chiara, but she thought
I was a bot."

21:36.240 --> 21:38.519
-It's not bad.
-It doesn't make sense.

21:38.559 --> 21:40.960
"Chiara thought I was rock'n'roll,"
and you,

21:41.039 --> 21:42.079
"But he's not."

21:42.559 --> 21:44.200
This is acceptable.

21:44.279 --> 21:47.400
Otherwise, I wanted to put something
about "the dog..."

21:47.480 --> 21:49.319
That would make more sense.

21:49.480 --> 21:53.039
Everything started
With a dog and a bow tie

21:53.160 --> 21:55.079
I think it's funnier like this.

21:55.240 --> 21:57.000
-How do you write...
-"Bow tie."

21:57.079 --> 22:00.160
We changed the first verse.
Is it called a verse?

22:00.240 --> 22:02.920
Because our followers know
how it all started,

22:03.039 --> 22:05.960
thanks to a piece of his song,

22:06.039 --> 22:09.880
so it has to do with my dog,
a bow tie, et cetera. So we put that

22:10.240 --> 22:11.920
for those who know us well.

22:12.279 --> 22:13.400
MoÃ«t & Chandon

22:13.480 --> 22:16.599
-Random.
-No, something like, "How about that."

22:16.680 --> 22:18.799
Yes! Wow! Oh, holy shit!

22:19.200 --> 22:23.680
She's the new Mogol, bloody hell! Yes!
"How about that," that's it, done.

22:23.759 --> 22:25.200
Well, it's not...

22:25.279 --> 22:27.720
Perfect, love. Colloquial, beautiful.

22:27.799 --> 22:30.599
The earnings of this hit
will be split fifty-fifty.

22:31.240 --> 22:32.640
So now he sings his parts?

22:32.720 --> 22:36.440
Yes, so then you can hear them
and overdub yours.

22:36.559 --> 22:38.359
One, two, three, Winnie the Pooh!

22:38.440 --> 22:40.400
-God.
-When you want. We're ready.

22:40.480 --> 22:41.480
Okay, go.

22:44.319 --> 22:46.039
Chia...

22:46.119 --> 22:47.680
Can you raise my voice?

22:47.759 --> 22:50.440
I'll lower the base and raise the voice.

22:50.519 --> 22:54.279
Everything started
With a dog and a bow tie

22:54.960 --> 22:58.720
And now we're expanding the family
A little more

22:59.480 --> 23:03.200
Because every time you kiss me
You knock me out

23:05.680 --> 23:07.680
And the show begins

23:07.759 --> 23:10.839
The Ferragnez

23:11.680 --> 23:15.559
-Did he have the autotune?
-Yes. But very light.

23:15.640 --> 23:17.599
I want it very strong, though.

23:18.200 --> 23:19.200
Okay.

23:19.279 --> 23:22.319
It's light and funny.
It's a theme song, right?

23:22.400 --> 23:23.759
-What's wrong?
-I'm nervous.

23:24.079 --> 23:28.240
You're not with Claudio Villa!
Come on, you see I suck too.

23:28.319 --> 23:29.319
All right.

23:31.240 --> 23:33.000
Will you come over there with me?

23:35.119 --> 23:37.000
Are you ashamed? Love!

23:37.079 --> 23:40.480
-There are a lot of people!
-How did you do the one with Baby K?

23:40.559 --> 23:42.319
-I was drunk.
-Were you?

23:42.400 --> 23:44.720
-You're pregnant now, you can't.
-Exactly.

23:44.799 --> 23:47.000
-Let's remove some bass tones.
-It was fun.

23:47.079 --> 23:50.839
She was a good coach.
We drank champagne before recording.

23:50.920 --> 23:54.480
-Oh, God.
-I was super chill.

23:54.960 --> 23:57.039
You need to have fun, love.

23:57.119 --> 23:59.880
Come on,
nothing is gonna happen, trust me.

24:01.759 --> 24:04.720
How do I sing?
Can you already put the autotune?

24:05.000 --> 24:06.480
-Autotune.
-Ready.

24:06.559 --> 24:07.599
Help.

24:07.680 --> 24:10.000
-What do I do now?
-Sing.

24:10.079 --> 24:12.119
-Okay, shall I start?
-No, wait!

24:12.200 --> 24:14.440
-I'm scared.
-Just try. Listen to me, go.

24:15.039 --> 24:17.640
-Let's do it together.
-But I can't hear it.

24:18.720 --> 24:22.000
Everything started
With a dog and a bow tie

24:22.079 --> 24:23.440
How about that

24:24.119 --> 24:26.079
How about that

24:26.160 --> 24:27.519
I can't do it that high!

24:27.599 --> 24:28.799
How about that

24:28.880 --> 24:31.519
You're a woman.
For me it's too high, I'm a baritone.

24:32.079 --> 24:35.759
-I don't know what that means!
-That I have a lower voice.

24:35.839 --> 24:37.799
How about that

24:37.880 --> 24:40.079
-Exactly.
-Push it a little bit more.

24:41.359 --> 24:42.400
Don't think.

24:43.519 --> 24:46.839
Everything started
With a dog and a bow tie

24:46.920 --> 24:48.119
How about that

24:54.839 --> 24:56.920
-Come here.
-You are not...

24:58.799 --> 25:00.599
It wasn't bad. Believe in it.

25:00.720 --> 25:02.799
-Well...
-You need to believe in it.

25:02.880 --> 25:05.799
If she believed a little a bit more,
she would rock.

25:05.920 --> 25:11.400
She gets nervous, it's fair. I get nervous
and I've been doing this for years.

25:12.039 --> 25:13.480
How about that

25:13.559 --> 25:16.559
And now we're expanding the family
A little more

25:16.640 --> 25:18.119
Like a yo-yo

25:18.200 --> 25:21.400
Because every time you kiss me
You knock me out

25:21.480 --> 25:25.799
So kiss me, silly
And the show begins

25:25.880 --> 25:27.480
The Ferragnez

25:27.559 --> 25:29.559
-Okay!
-Good.

25:29.640 --> 25:31.559
-Let's go listen.
-Let's go.

25:31.880 --> 25:34.279
God, it's too hard doing this stuff.

25:35.319 --> 25:38.200
Why can't I sing? I wanted to be a singer.

25:38.279 --> 25:41.599
What if we ask Arisa to sing?
We say it's Chiara.

25:42.480 --> 25:44.720
-It wasn't easy.
-No, it wasn't!

25:44.799 --> 25:45.720
You rocked.

25:47.599 --> 25:49.279
-Nice!
-Well, so-so.

25:49.920 --> 25:52.119
We need to understand
if you're out of tune.

25:57.799 --> 25:59.200
They sound like sirens.

26:02.920 --> 26:04.160
Oh God, come on!

26:04.720 --> 26:08.079
I got this award for the theme song
before it even came out

26:08.160 --> 26:11.319
and this shows my potential as a singer.

26:11.640 --> 26:14.359
Let's avoid giving spoilers
about this one too.

26:16.400 --> 26:18.759
-No!
-No, I can't believe it.

26:18.839 --> 26:20.519
I'll delete it right away.

26:20.599 --> 26:23.119
-You made me press with my finger!
-I didn't!

26:23.200 --> 26:24.720
Fuck!

26:24.799 --> 26:27.119
-He was about to--
-No! I'm deleting it.

26:27.839 --> 26:31.160
All good, guys, all good. Nobody saw it.

26:32.079 --> 26:35.039
Now I'll have my revenge
because Fede will try

26:35.119 --> 26:39.000
the pain of childbirth,
even if I don't think it will be

26:39.240 --> 26:44.279
as devastating and painful as the real
thing, but he'll get an idea, at least.

26:44.359 --> 26:45.559
Okay.

26:45.640 --> 26:51.359
Another couple of friends of mine,
Lorenzo and Martina, will try it too.

26:51.440 --> 26:55.559
-Are you nervous?
-No, I don't know what I have to do.

26:55.640 --> 26:56.799
Suffer.

26:56.880 --> 27:02.359
Martina is expecting twin girls.
She's a close friend of mine, it'll be fun

27:02.480 --> 27:04.720
to see who will handle it better.

27:04.839 --> 27:07.720
I think Lorenzo will win,
Fede can't take much pain.

27:07.839 --> 27:09.119
Hello!

27:09.200 --> 27:10.960
-Hello, love!
-How are you?

27:11.039 --> 27:12.319
Good.

27:12.400 --> 27:15.319
-Are you ready, Lori?
-Super ready.

27:15.400 --> 27:18.000
-You can't run away, you're gonna do it.
-You sure?

27:18.079 --> 27:21.440
-What the fuck are we supposed to do?
-Assimilate their pain.

27:21.559 --> 27:23.319
Which will never be like ours.

27:23.400 --> 27:24.880
Yeah, we'll see.

27:24.960 --> 27:26.400
-There we go.
-Please.

27:26.480 --> 27:28.119
-Hello.
-Hi!

27:28.200 --> 27:30.200
-Welcome.
-Thank you so much.

27:30.279 --> 27:33.000
-Thank you. Hi, everyone.
-Wow!

27:33.079 --> 27:37.480
Is this a service you offer
to make men feel the pain of childbirth?

27:37.559 --> 27:42.039
Exactly. For this treatment
you should wear the scrubs on the beds.

27:42.160 --> 27:43.400
I love it.

27:43.920 --> 27:46.640
I love all of this. So cool.

27:47.039 --> 27:52.119
-I've never felt this pain. You did.
-I did, with the contractions.

27:52.200 --> 27:55.000
-Okay, I'm turning the machine on.
-No, hey!

27:55.079 --> 27:57.160
He hasn't attached it to you yet.

27:57.240 --> 27:59.440
This will be divided in three phases.

27:59.519 --> 28:04.279
The first phase will simulate
the preparatory contractions,

28:04.359 --> 28:09.839
the second phase will be the start of the
labor, with slightly longer contractions,

28:09.920 --> 28:15.920
and in the last phase the contraction will
be even longer, and closer to one another.

28:16.119 --> 28:17.799
And much stronger.

28:17.880 --> 28:21.119
Okay, we can proceed
with the electrode application.

28:21.200 --> 28:26.079
-When I had them, you were sleeping.
-It was night! What was I supposed to do?

28:26.160 --> 28:27.799
On the couch, sleeping.

28:27.880 --> 28:29.759
-Can you sit up, please?
-Yes.

28:29.839 --> 28:32.599
It's only fair
that he takes his share, now.

28:32.680 --> 28:34.640
-Come on, love.
-Okay.

28:34.720 --> 28:38.720
-You can lay back down.
-I'll take some souvenir pictures of you.

28:39.599 --> 28:43.519
-Lori, any comments?
-Let's just hope it all goes well.

28:43.640 --> 28:49.200
-Let's hope it's a girl.
-No, wait a minute, guys. I'd like...

28:49.720 --> 28:52.559
-Can't I see what happens to him first?
-Fuck no!

28:52.640 --> 28:56.400
-If anything, the other way around.
-Is it simultaneous?

28:56.480 --> 28:57.519
Simultaneous? No!

28:58.119 --> 28:59.279
Let's hold hands.

29:00.400 --> 29:03.359
-No, guys, I can't do it!
-Come on, don't be--

29:03.440 --> 29:06.440
-I'm having a panic attack.
-Don't panic, jeez!

29:06.519 --> 29:10.720
When you give birth,
I'll treat you like this. Come here.

29:10.799 --> 29:12.920
-What do I have to do?
-Give me support.

29:13.000 --> 29:15.720
-I'm starting to feel...
-It's already started.

29:15.799 --> 29:17.160
No, oh!

29:17.240 --> 29:22.720
-Ouch, you're hurting my hand, Lorenzo.
-He's also ice cold.

29:29.680 --> 29:33.240
-Nice start, isn't it?
-What the fuck are we doing?

29:35.799 --> 29:37.160
We poor women.

29:37.720 --> 29:41.039
-This really makes you empathize.
-You can do it, you're a beast!

29:41.119 --> 29:42.880
-Like you told me.
-Okay.

29:43.279 --> 29:44.640
Which phase is this one?

29:44.720 --> 29:47.680
-The second one.
-The first phase of labor begins.

29:47.759 --> 29:50.240
Come on. Labor. Come on, love.

29:50.319 --> 29:52.920
-No, please!
-What do you feel?

29:53.000 --> 29:55.880
-Now it's a bit stronger than before.
-Fucking hell!

29:58.200 --> 30:01.480
-How fucking long does it last?
-Make sure you breathe.

30:01.559 --> 30:04.079
-Breathe, love.
-But it's lasting so long.

30:04.160 --> 30:06.240
With Chiara they didn't last this long!

30:06.319 --> 30:09.039
-They last longer than one minute!
-It's not true.

30:09.799 --> 30:12.799
-Son of a bitch!
-Come on, honey.

30:14.079 --> 30:17.440
-Think about what you're creating.
-It hurts more when I laugh!

30:18.640 --> 30:21.119
You're hurting me, Lore, fuck!

30:27.599 --> 30:29.920
Come on, guys, we're nearly there!

30:30.839 --> 30:34.000
It's a mix of humiliation and pain.

30:34.079 --> 30:35.640
It's horrible.

30:40.160 --> 30:41.519
But what is--

30:42.079 --> 30:44.200
No, no, no!

30:44.640 --> 30:46.359
No! I can't do it.

30:46.440 --> 30:47.839
-Come on!
-Gimme your hand.

30:47.920 --> 30:50.200
-You're a man.
-This one is stronger!

30:50.279 --> 30:54.920
You're hurting me, no, Lorenzo,
you're hurting me, ouch!

30:55.000 --> 30:59.440
-Aren't we done with this fucking labor?
-Last one.

30:59.519 --> 31:01.319
-Go, breathe.
-Don't blow!

31:01.400 --> 31:03.880
-What the fuck are you blowing?
-I'm not!

31:03.960 --> 31:05.480
-Come on, honey!
-Breathe.

31:05.559 --> 31:09.359
-Now there's the ejection.
-We'll prep you for phase three.

31:09.440 --> 31:13.559
It's going to simulate the last pushes,
the ones that are a bit lower.

31:13.640 --> 31:16.079
-We're ready.
-Give birth to these creatures.

31:17.640 --> 31:20.440
No, no, no!

31:20.519 --> 31:24.119
-Stop! I can't do it.
-It's nature, you can't say stop!

31:26.920 --> 31:31.400
I can't do it, I can't... Fuck!

31:31.759 --> 31:35.000
-No, honey, I can't do it.
-Come on, honey, come on!

31:36.160 --> 31:37.839
This thing is not gonna air.

31:40.039 --> 31:42.680
Come on, honey, I can see the head!

31:42.759 --> 31:44.960
-Give it all now.
-I can't do it anymore.

31:45.039 --> 31:48.240
-Come on, honey.
-No! Stop!

31:48.319 --> 31:54.279
Stop, stop! If you make it stronger
I'll pull everything off.

31:54.359 --> 31:56.519
-Come on!
-Fuck off!

32:01.680 --> 32:04.960
-Well done, honey!
-Fist bump, bro! Let's be men.

32:05.599 --> 32:08.720
-Well done.
-Good job, you gave birth!

32:09.119 --> 32:09.960
How was it?

32:10.039 --> 32:11.799
Terrible, fuck!

32:11.880 --> 32:13.319
-Damn!
-You did great.

32:13.400 --> 32:15.440
You both got to the end.

32:15.519 --> 32:16.640
Yes, exactly.

32:16.720 --> 32:18.799
I'll remove the ones on the back.

32:18.880 --> 32:20.559
-We came out well, Lore.
-Yes.

32:20.640 --> 32:24.519
I'm sure
I had a very dignified labor reaction.

32:24.680 --> 32:26.279
Love, turn around.

32:27.119 --> 32:30.039
-Guys, you were amazing.
-Thanks.

32:33.640 --> 32:36.359
After realizing
that you can support each other

32:36.440 --> 32:40.480
and that you can put yourself
in each other's shoes, I have a proposal.

32:41.079 --> 32:44.720
I'd like to meet you individually
next time.

32:44.799 --> 32:47.599
I'd like to be able
to meet only with you, Chiara,

32:47.680 --> 32:50.880
and have the opportunity
to speak only with you, Federico.

32:51.319 --> 32:53.480
And I think we'll have fun.

32:55.680 --> 32:57.039
